headline: Barclays ups price targets for Seagate, Western Digital on improved HDD outlook
summary: Investing.com -- Barclays has raised its price targets for Seagate Technology and Western Digital, pointing to improved demand trends and firmer pricing in the hard disk drive (HDD) market.
